Documentation    •    PyPI    •    Source Code <p>A Python library for email management. Connect to any IMAP/SMTP server, read and send emails, sync your mailbox to a local database, and restore backups — all with a single, unified API.</p> Python 3.8+ <pre><code>"""Read your unread mail in 4 lines."""

from email_profile import Email


def main() -&gt; None:
    with Email.from_env() as app:
        for msg in app.unread().messages():
            print(f"{msg.date}  {msg.from_:&lt;40}  {msg.subject}")


if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
